data.description: Gladstone Landing is offering a 55 and better community in its closeout phase with 1 luxury floor plan left. This stunning Hartwell Model Home floor plan is an end unit that features three bedrooms, master on the main level with walk-in closet, open kitchen concept to the family room with fireplace, SS appliances, separate dining room, large loft upstairs and a covered back porch. Also refrigerator and washer/dryer included in the sale. We are conveniently located near the Summit Chase Country Club. Minutes from Shoppes of Webb Gin and restaurants. HOA includes lawn care and exterior maintenance. $5,000 toward closing cost when using our preferred lender. Call today for more details.
